"""
    ``generate_eline_list``: search all lines
    """
assert generate_eline_list(elements, incident_energy=incident_energy
    ) == elines, 'Emission line list is generated incorrectly'
pytest.mark.parametrize('elements, incident_energy, elines', [(['Fe', 'W',
    'Ta'], 12.0, ['Fe_K', 'W_L', 'W_M', 'Ta_L', 'Ta_M']), (['Fe', 'W', 'Ta'
    ], 6.0, ['W_M', 'Ta_M'])])
